Action.author: wlahti
Action.body: That logging message was actually related to the CORE_LOGGING_ERROR setting (which was used for the error handling framework) so it was an expected log message at the time. However, this setting has been removed via https://gerrit.hyperledger.org/r/#/c/8581/ (merged on April 26). Can you grab the latest code and ensure that this item can be closed?
